      "id": "body.solutions_system-integrators.p.1",
      "en": "Transform your consulting business with sovereign cloud infrastructure that you can brand, customize, and scale. Elemento empowers system integrators to deliver enterprise-grade cloud environments under their own brand while maintaining complete control and recurring revenue.",
